Find the first case for each country in the dataset

firstcase <- all_countries_seg %>% 
  dplyr::select(Country, Date, Confirmed) %>% 
  filter(Confirmed > 1) %>% 
  group_by(Country) %>% 
  summarise(min_case = min(Confirmed), Date = first(Date))
